long_desc.thetext:
Playground example:

var l = new qx.ui.layout.Atom();
l.setCenter(true);
var c = new qx.ui.container.Composite(l);
c.setBackgroundColor("#eee");
this.getRoot().add(c);

var w1 = new qx.ui.core.Widget().set({backgroundColor: "red", height: 50});
var w2 = new qx.ui.core.Widget().set({backgroundColor: "blue", height: 50});
c.setHeight(200);
c.add(w1);
c.add(w2);

Expected behavior:
The widgets should be vertically centered and retain their height.

Observed behavior:
The widgets' top edge is aligned with the middle of the container and they receive the container's height so they're partially cut off.
